lead_paragraph: Chinese wild-card entry Zhang Shuai became the first player to secure a semifinal spot at the WTA Elite Trophy tournament, beating Timea Babos 7-6 (2), 6-4 on Thursday to secure the top spot in her group with two wins.

headline.print_headline: Chinese Wildcard Zhang Secures Spot in Elite Trophy Semis
